there was a little girl who lived in a village near the forest.  She was a good little girl, and wanted to go out into the world and help others.  But her mother said she must be careful not to talk to strangers or go out alone.  One morning she heard a rustling in the trees behind her, and she turned around to see what was making the noise.  She saw a strange little man looking down at her.  "Good morning," said the little man
